    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="VALI_KHAN_0-1742972268216.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/242606i506E301F84239FCB/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="VALI_KHAN_0-1742972268216.png" alt="VALI_KHAN_0-1742972268216.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Dear All,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I would appreciate your help in understanding how to dynamically set values for multiple input fields within a loop. &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Scenario: I have several input fields that follow an incremental naming pattern.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;InputField1&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;InputField2&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;InputField3&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;InputField4&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I want to loop through these fields and assign values to them dynamically.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="VALI_KHAN_1-1742972816961.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/242607i256F2AD25ADDF2FB/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="VALI_KHAN_1-1742972816961.png" alt="VALI_KHAN_1-1742972816961.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thank you for your assistance!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Details- I want to automate a website to extract the PO Number and input the corresponding details such as Ship Date, Order Total, Agent Name, and more. I need to do this repeatedly within a single loop. While other RPA tools can accomplish this, I am having trouble with SAP BPA. I would appreciate any guidance, best practices, or example implementations for managing&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;dynamic UI elements&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;in SAP BPA.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Page link-(&lt;A href="https://pathfinder.automationanywhere.com/challenges/automationanywherelabs-supplychainmanagement.html?" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://pathfinder.automationanywhere.com/challenges/automationanywherelabs-supplychainmanagement.html?&lt;/A&gt;)&lt;/P&gt;</content>
